47,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生得樣衰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺呢個係主要原因，生得靚仔講野都可以大聲啲，同沒女神探講既一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e9f07e594d6c0ab8830f5c28a11359bbf9ffc6","tid":29054,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:02:40.000Z","msg":"跌左杯雪糕"},{"pid":"f6fc82f10280fc76607da0749f0ee57edd799dd2","tid":29054,"uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等一個新環境 新人事 新變遷 <br />\n你就會放得開 <br />\n以一種新習慣蓋過舊習慣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n目前好難轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好彩我過場過得快<br />\n係呢段時間搵下自己興趣 思考下人生啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我仲要每日面對，起碼仲有2個學期，點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4701fe4b5af4da44a8845d83c74032b2c392f24b","tid":29054,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"俾丫媽鬧我仆街仔，果下真係覺得人生無晒意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9b9b066d7834f2281493ca539862ff37624cb6","tid":29054,"uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾丫媽鬧我仆街仔，果下真係覺得人生無晒意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n碎料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c447f1141436e325eae837858372ebb21dc04aa4","tid":29054,"uid":9856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"佢生活多姿多采 我淡然無味 但佢冇體諒我仲話返我轉頭"},{"pid":"b41e599bd2c67944dc6cb9d911bb20605b4d8098","tid":29054,"uid":37739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"被多次傷害，仍抱有希望，到最後仍然俾機會佢，直到絕望 <img src=\"/ass